      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW TIFFY (7) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, holding on for a minor placing when second and beaten 1.75 lengths at Warrnambool over 390m in 22.05. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Key chance in this line up. PAW JUDD (1) was in the minors two back (22.24) at this track but ran below best last time at Geelong, finishing 7th. Must be included in calculations. PAW BRODY (8) ran good time (22.57) winning a Grade 4/5 three back at Warragul but missed the frame latest finishing sixth at Ballarat. Has the ability and expected to do much better. SUNNY STRIDE (2) in the money here last time and looks a top-three prospect again.",
